WEBVTT

00:00:10.438 --> 00:00:13.313
Pangu separated heaven and earth.
All things flourished.

00:00:15.021 --> 00:00:18.188
Thousands of years ago,
demonic flames sundered the land.

00:00:18.271 --> 00:00:20.771
The Demon King of the Sixth Heaven
entered the Human Realm.

00:00:21.396 --> 00:00:24.563
He fed on the living to enhance his power,

00:00:24.646 --> 00:00:26.771
desiring to become the supreme overlord.

00:00:28.521 --> 00:00:31.605
The Celestial Realm sent its
fiercest warrior, the Third Crown Prince,

00:00:31.688 --> 00:00:33.396
to subdue the demon.

00:00:33.896 --> 00:00:36.605
The ensuing battle was earth-shattering.

00:00:37.146 --> 00:00:39.563
The Demon King was driven back to hell.

00:00:40.146 --> 00:00:43.355
But the battle
left the Human Realm in ruins.

00:00:43.896 --> 00:00:46.230
So the Celestial Realm
prohibited gods and demons

00:00:46.313 --> 00:00:48.896
from entering the Human Realm
in their true forms.

00:00:49.396 --> 00:00:53.063
Henceforth, any god or demon
who wishes to enter the Human Realm

00:00:54.146 --> 00:00:57.063
must use spirit channeling
to circumvent this ban.

00:00:59.021 --> 00:01:01.146
However,
very few people in the Human Realm

00:01:01.688 --> 00:01:03.688
can forge covenants
with gods and demons

00:01:05.438 --> 00:01:07.271
and become supernatural agents.

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:26.771
Among those who do,

00:01:26.855 --> 00:01:29.855
some are endowed with immense power
and grave duties.

00:01:31.396 --> 00:01:32.480
They are called…

00:01:35.563 --> 00:01:36.605
agents from above.

00:01:36.688 --> 00:01:38.521
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:42.396 --> 00:01:47.188
THE SINNER

00:01:54.646 --> 00:02:00.980
DONGFENG MARKET

00:02:24.730 --> 00:02:25.563
Excuse me,

00:02:25.646 --> 00:02:26.730
do you know…

00:02:39.605 --> 00:02:40.980
Stop if you're human.

00:02:43.188 --> 00:02:45.188
Enter if you're a ghost.

00:03:51.021 --> 00:03:54.688
MASTER HAN CHIEH
409, NO. 56, LN. 114, DONGFENG ST., TAIPEI

00:04:16.438 --> 00:04:19.063
409, NO. 56, LN. 114, DONGFENG ST.

00:04:25.438 --> 00:04:27.688
-Who is it?
-I'm looking for Han Chieh.

00:04:41.646 --> 00:04:42.563
What do you want?

00:04:43.980 --> 00:04:45.605
Hi, Master Han. I'm Leafy.

00:04:45.688 --> 00:04:48.021
I heard you specialize
in ghost-related issues.

00:04:48.105 --> 00:04:50.521
-Sorry, I don't take new clients.
-Hey, wait.

00:04:50.605 --> 00:04:52.896
I know you only work
for the Third Crown Prince.

00:04:52.980 --> 00:04:54.980
But I have no one else to turn to.

00:04:56.813 --> 00:04:58.980
Someone put this under my dad's pillow.

00:04:59.813 --> 00:05:01.521
A female ghost enchanted him.

00:05:06.146 --> 00:05:08.188
Go away. Don't bother me again.

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:18.730
What's wrong with you? Go home.

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.271
What's with your attitude?

00:05:22.355 --> 00:05:25.063
Some great master,
more like a scamming lowlife!

00:05:25.646 --> 00:05:27.355
I told you to go home, hear me?

00:06:02.563 --> 00:06:03.396
-Hey.
-Come on.

00:06:06.271 --> 00:06:07.188
What're you doing?

00:07:05.938 --> 00:07:08.063
Little girl, how old are you?

00:07:08.563 --> 00:07:09.396
I'm 21.

00:07:18.938 --> 00:07:20.438
When's your next day off?

00:07:21.230 --> 00:07:22.188
I'm not sure.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:25.105
She's only 21.

00:07:25.188 --> 00:07:26.855
Be gentle with her.

00:07:26.938 --> 00:07:28.688
Or the heavens might punish you.

00:07:29.730 --> 00:07:30.855
I'm off.

00:07:31.688 --> 00:07:33.230
I'll come round when I'm free.

00:07:51.813 --> 00:07:53.396
Stupid bird. What now?

00:07:59.855 --> 00:08:02.480
I've got so many tasks.
And you won't let me smoke.

00:08:02.563 --> 00:08:03.438
Give me a break.

00:08:05.396 --> 00:08:06.646
Thank you.

00:08:17.646 --> 00:08:18.730
Master Han.

00:08:21.813 --> 00:08:23.813
My mom's
been seeing a feng shui master.

00:08:23.896 --> 00:08:27.063
He knows we've got money,
and is using this to hurt my dad.

00:08:27.146 --> 00:08:27.980
It's fake.

00:08:28.771 --> 00:08:29.646
It's real.

00:08:30.230 --> 00:08:31.563
I've seen it more than once.

00:08:31.646 --> 00:08:32.646
WUMENG OCCULTIST…

00:08:32.730 --> 00:08:35.438
Says he's a master
of the Wumeng Maoshan Technique.

00:08:38.563 --> 00:08:39.521
Wumeng Maoshan?

00:08:48.980 --> 00:08:50.563
HO CHUN-LAI

00:08:51.813 --> 00:08:55.355
SOLE HEIR OF WUMENG MAOSHAN TRADITION
DISCIPLE OF MASTER CHEN CHI-SHA

00:09:00.896 --> 00:09:04.271
WUMENG OCCULTIST USES
FEMALE GHOSTS TO TARGET FAMILY

00:09:04.355 --> 00:09:07.480
SOLE HEIR OF WUMENG MAOSHAN TRADITION

00:09:10.188 --> 00:09:12.396
-You should've shown me sooner.
-You know him?

00:09:14.646 --> 00:09:15.480
No, not him.

00:09:16.605 --> 00:09:17.605
MASTER CHEN CHI-SHA

00:09:17.688 --> 00:09:20.063
But his master, Chen Chi-sha,
is pretty famous.

00:09:26.688 --> 00:09:30.021
Seems your family's in trouble.
I've just gotten orders from above.

00:09:30.105 --> 00:09:31.896
From the Third Crown Prince?

00:09:34.146 --> 00:09:35.855
I'll take a look tomorrow.

00:09:36.355 --> 00:09:37.605
Thank you, Master Han.

00:09:38.521 --> 00:09:39.855
Don't call me "Master".

00:09:40.355 --> 00:09:42.480
I said I'd take a look,
not take the job.

00:09:43.521 --> 00:09:44.355
Yes, Mr. Han.

00:09:46.438 --> 00:09:48.230
What was all that outside just now?

00:09:51.688 --> 00:09:55.021
Some asshole had relationship troubles
here a few years back.

00:09:56.146 --> 00:09:57.980
He started a fire to end it all.

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:00.021
But the asshole survived.

00:10:00.730 --> 00:10:02.563
The residents here weren't so lucky.

00:10:03.521 --> 00:10:04.730
As they died unjustly,

00:10:04.813 --> 00:10:08.480
most of them became earthbound spirits
and got stuck here.

00:10:09.646 --> 00:10:13.313
Every night after 11 p.m.,
they get real spooked out.

00:10:13.813 --> 00:10:15.146
They think he'll come back

00:10:15.230 --> 00:10:18.313
and set fire to the place again.
Like you saw earlier.

00:10:19.605 --> 00:10:20.438
Get it?

00:10:27.980 --> 00:10:30.230
Mr. Han, what was that for?

00:10:38.396 --> 00:10:41.063
Opening your third eye
so you don't spook my neighbors.

00:10:59.688 --> 00:11:01.813
They're your neighbors?

00:11:04.605 --> 00:11:06.563
It's fine, nothing to be afraid of.

00:11:24.063 --> 00:11:25.521
Sorry to disturb you.

00:11:31.355 --> 00:11:34.230
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

00:11:34.813 --> 00:11:37.813
I can't,
she's in tears just talking about it.

00:11:37.896 --> 00:11:39.563
Sir, don't wire the money yet.

00:11:39.646 --> 00:11:41.105
Do nothing at the bank.

00:11:41.188 --> 00:11:43.480
Let the police handle it
when they arrive.

00:11:43.563 --> 00:11:45.813
But what if
my overseas girlfriend dumps me?

00:11:45.896 --> 00:11:48.688
Damn it. I'm not a god, how should I know?

00:11:48.771 --> 00:11:52.605
She told you to ignore the police.
Only scammers say that, sir.

00:11:52.688 --> 00:11:54.480
-What we have is true love.
-Sir.

00:11:55.146 --> 00:11:57.730
Sir. Hey, sir.

00:11:59.021 --> 00:12:01.855
Goddammit, he won't listen.

00:12:08.271 --> 00:12:09.605
Restroom Peeping Tom.

00:12:09.688 --> 00:12:11.688
No one shows up on the security cam.

00:12:12.230 --> 00:12:15.105
Have Han Chieh look into it.
See if it's a ghost.

00:12:16.021 --> 00:12:18.521
No filthy spirits escape my spirit vision.

00:12:19.605 --> 00:12:20.438
As if.

00:12:20.521 --> 00:12:23.188
You were just born
with the ability to see them.

00:12:23.271 --> 00:12:27.021
You're on this case to make you useful.

00:12:27.646 --> 00:12:29.813
Don't worry, Chao. Leave this to me.

00:12:29.896 --> 00:12:33.313
If I can handle these old-timers,
what's a few ghosts?

00:12:45.021 --> 00:12:47.521
The first time I saw her,
she was standing there.

00:12:49.271 --> 00:12:51.605
The second time,
she was standing there.

00:13:13.230 --> 00:13:15.355
MY JAPAN TRIP
I'LL BE BACK WHEN I'M BETTER

00:13:15.438 --> 00:13:19.188
LEAFY, YOU CAN DO IT!
GET WELL SOON

00:13:22.438 --> 00:13:27.438
BEI KANG UNITED HOSPITAL, YEH CHIH-LING

00:13:31.563 --> 00:13:33.230
Hey. Not in here.

00:13:40.313 --> 00:13:41.396
Are you okay?

00:13:43.188 --> 00:13:45.105
I'm fine. It's just leukemia.

00:13:53.063 --> 00:13:54.646
Look. Pretty cool, right?

00:14:02.063 --> 00:14:02.896
Yeah.

00:14:06.938 --> 00:14:08.355
I found the red envelope here.

00:14:12.521 --> 00:14:14.563
Look, another one.

00:14:27.938 --> 00:14:30.146
I don't smell anything. It's a fake.

00:14:30.230 --> 00:14:32.438
That's not possible. I know I saw her.

00:14:32.521 --> 00:14:35.855
If there really was a ghost,
I'd be able to see her and smell her.

00:14:37.563 --> 00:14:39.813
But I don't smell a thing
on this red envelope.

00:14:39.896 --> 00:14:41.063
Maybe you imagined it?

00:14:42.938 --> 00:14:43.896
In here, Master Ho.

00:14:45.063 --> 00:14:46.605
Sorry for troubling you again.

00:14:47.646 --> 00:14:48.730
Here, this way.

00:14:48.813 --> 00:14:49.730
Chih-ling.

00:14:50.855 --> 00:14:52.021
You have company?

00:14:52.521 --> 00:14:53.396
-Yes.
-Hello.

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:55.021
He studies film at college too.

00:14:55.855 --> 00:14:58.438
I asked Master Ho
to check how you're doing today.

00:14:58.521 --> 00:15:00.938
Have a seat. I'll get some fruit.

00:15:01.480 --> 00:15:02.396
Give me a hand.

00:15:03.438 --> 00:15:04.271
Please sit.

00:15:07.771 --> 00:15:10.105
So, Master Ho,
you're an expert on feng shui

00:15:10.188 --> 00:15:11.105
and sick girls.

00:15:12.938 --> 00:15:14.355
I came to read her palms

00:15:14.438 --> 00:15:17.396
to see how she can avoid her doom.

00:15:17.480 --> 00:15:18.355
Avoid doom?

00:15:19.230 --> 00:15:20.646
By putting this here?

00:15:22.521 --> 00:15:23.605
How's Chen Chi-sha?

00:15:25.146 --> 00:15:27.063
Master Chen retired years ago.

00:15:27.146 --> 00:15:29.438
He spends his time in the sun
enjoying life.

00:15:30.355 --> 00:15:32.896
This red envelope
helps thwart extramarital affairs,

00:15:32.980 --> 00:15:35.855
so Mrs. Yeh can save her marriage.

00:15:35.938 --> 00:15:38.605
I know all about
the Wumeng Maoshan Technique.

00:15:39.188 --> 00:15:42.313
So I'm warning you not to harm them.

00:15:45.813 --> 00:15:46.980
Young man.

00:15:47.063 --> 00:15:50.271
They pay me to alleviate their woes.

00:15:51.688 --> 00:15:53.563
Why would I wish them harm?

00:16:03.105 --> 00:16:04.188
WUMENG OCCULTIST USES

00:16:04.271 --> 00:16:05.855
FEMALE GHOSTS TO TARGET FAMILY

00:16:05.938 --> 00:16:07.188
GHOST HAUNTS LADIES' ROOM

00:16:12.563 --> 00:16:14.771
Han Chieh, I don't trust that guy.

00:16:15.563 --> 00:16:18.646
Why are you here again?
Shouldn't you be at home resting?

00:16:22.021 --> 00:16:24.063
I told my mom we're making a movie.

00:16:24.146 --> 00:16:26.105
She actually agreed to let me out.

00:16:27.563 --> 00:16:30.105
Find someone else to hang out with.
I'm busy.

00:16:31.271 --> 00:16:32.438
Doing what?

00:16:33.021 --> 00:16:34.688
Did you get new instructions?

00:16:34.771 --> 00:16:36.605
Can I tag along?

00:16:43.063 --> 00:16:45.730
My house is still haunted.

00:16:45.813 --> 00:16:47.771
Really gonna just ditch me like this?

00:16:49.396 --> 00:16:53.105
That'd make me sad.
I'll start crying and make a scene.

00:16:53.563 --> 00:16:56.605
People will think we're a couple fighting.

00:17:00.938 --> 00:17:03.188
A new friend?
Won't you introduce us?

00:17:05.021 --> 00:17:07.521
Not like that.
She's a client. We're not close.

00:17:07.605 --> 00:17:09.271
Hi, we're friends.

00:17:12.688 --> 00:17:15.021
Chieh is my neighbor.
His friend is my friend.

00:17:15.521 --> 00:17:17.646
-What'll it be?
-The usual, pork rice bowl.

00:17:17.730 --> 00:17:18.896
One more.

00:17:20.771 --> 00:17:21.813
Okay.

00:17:32.271 --> 00:17:33.271
And she is…

00:17:35.855 --> 00:17:38.855
Hey, that's messed up. Is she even 18?

00:17:39.688 --> 00:17:41.980
My house is haunted.
I asked him for help.

00:17:42.063 --> 00:17:44.063
What a coincidence.
I need his help too.

00:17:44.146 --> 00:17:45.230
Eaten yet?

00:17:45.313 --> 00:17:48.605
Not yet.
So you'd better not ruin my appetite.

00:17:50.813 --> 00:17:52.021
Look at a case for me.

00:17:52.855 --> 00:17:53.688
Why should I?

00:17:54.271 --> 00:17:56.438
'Cause you're a model citizen
helping the cops.

00:17:56.521 --> 00:17:58.855
-Do I look like a model citizen?
-Yeah.

00:17:58.938 --> 00:18:01.563
A really handsome one.
I'll treat you to bubble tea.

00:18:01.646 --> 00:18:03.605
Thanks, uncle officer.

00:18:03.688 --> 00:18:05.021
Uncle?

00:18:05.105 --> 00:18:06.355
I mean, officer.

00:18:07.271 --> 00:18:08.855
Sister Lo, three bubble teas!

00:18:13.355 --> 00:18:14.480
-A Peeping Tom?
-Yeah.

00:18:15.063 --> 00:18:18.896
Four reports this month of a pervert
harassing girls at an internet cafe.

00:18:19.521 --> 00:18:22.396
There is nobody in the footage.
It has to be a ghost.

00:18:24.646 --> 00:18:26.646
-So you came to see me?
-Yeah.

00:18:28.980 --> 00:18:31.438
GHOST HAUNTS LADIES' ROOM

00:18:33.021 --> 00:18:35.313
I've got instructions from above.
I'm on it.

00:18:36.271 --> 00:18:37.146
-I'll go too.
-No.

00:18:37.230 --> 00:18:39.230
Your masculinity
will scare the ghost off.

00:18:39.313 --> 00:18:40.605
-Then I'll go.
-No way.

00:18:41.688 --> 00:18:42.563
You're too young.

00:18:47.188 --> 00:18:48.021
You can come.

00:19:12.146 --> 00:19:14.896
Hey! Show some respect.

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:17.813
How can you watch that stuff
in front of me?

00:19:17.896 --> 00:19:19.813
It's not for you.
It's for the Peeping Tom.

00:19:20.396 --> 00:19:23.438
Seeing a girl watching porn
might lure him out.

00:19:24.396 --> 00:19:26.521
What kind of dumbass move is that?

00:19:27.146 --> 00:19:30.480
You'd better earn your keep.
Turn on all the computers.

00:19:31.271 --> 00:19:32.521
We'll bait the pervert.

00:19:53.146 --> 00:19:53.980
Han Chieh.

00:19:54.896 --> 00:19:57.646
Why'd you become
the Third Crown Prince's agent?

00:20:03.105 --> 00:20:05.730
Hey, you already know about my wig.

00:20:05.813 --> 00:20:07.480
You should open up to me too.

00:20:10.813 --> 00:20:11.855
For my family.

00:20:12.355 --> 00:20:13.271
Family?

00:20:13.355 --> 00:20:14.438
Where are they?

00:20:19.188 --> 00:20:20.146
In hell.

00:20:24.855 --> 00:20:27.480
When I was young, I made a huge mistake

00:20:28.063 --> 00:20:29.271
and got them killed.

00:20:30.271 --> 00:20:31.688
So I decided to kill myself.

00:21:08.605 --> 00:21:09.438
Hey.

00:21:12.521 --> 00:21:16.563
Think jumping off some building
and dying would fix everything?

00:21:19.146 --> 00:21:19.980
Kid.

00:21:20.688 --> 00:21:23.563
You got my aide killed.
How are you going to repay me?

00:21:24.146 --> 00:21:25.855
I…

00:21:26.355 --> 00:21:27.646
Who was your assistant?

00:21:28.438 --> 00:21:29.271
Your dad.

00:21:32.896 --> 00:21:34.480
Your dad was my assistant.

00:21:35.146 --> 00:21:36.813
So what's it going to be?

00:21:38.230 --> 00:21:39.063
My dad?

00:21:40.146 --> 00:21:40.980
I…

00:21:41.480 --> 00:21:42.730
Take my life instead.

00:21:43.230 --> 00:21:44.063
Okay?

00:21:46.230 --> 00:21:47.480
Your lousy life

00:21:48.146 --> 00:21:51.146
is even lousier than the rag
your dad cleaned the table with.

00:21:51.896 --> 00:21:54.230
Take your life? It's not that simple.

00:22:35.771 --> 00:22:36.980
Dad!

00:22:37.438 --> 00:22:38.480
Mom!

00:22:39.355 --> 00:22:42.146
This is what you humans call hell.

00:22:42.688 --> 00:22:45.188
Your parents didn't raise you properly.

00:22:45.271 --> 00:22:47.480
So they'll be punished in your place

00:22:47.563 --> 00:22:49.355
until you atone for their sins.

00:22:53.146 --> 00:22:54.563
It was my mistake.

00:22:55.563 --> 00:22:56.438
Let them out.

00:22:56.938 --> 00:22:58.605
Take me instead. Take me.

00:23:00.146 --> 00:23:02.355
That's not going to happen.

00:23:03.271 --> 00:23:05.271
But we can negotiate terms.

00:23:05.355 --> 00:23:07.855
Make life a bit easier for them in there.

00:23:09.063 --> 00:23:09.896
Okay.

00:23:13.271 --> 00:23:15.521
I'll do anything you want. Anything.

00:23:17.271 --> 00:23:18.980
I'll do anything you want.

00:23:23.855 --> 00:23:25.063
Who exactly are you?

00:23:30.605 --> 00:23:31.688
You've forgotten me?

00:23:32.646 --> 00:23:36.896
I'm that handsome guy you've worshiped

00:23:38.313 --> 00:23:39.980
since you were a kid.

00:23:47.855 --> 00:23:48.771
Third Crown Prince.

00:23:52.021 --> 00:23:53.271
Is it really you?

00:23:55.355 --> 00:23:57.896
Kid, you got your dad killed.

00:23:58.521 --> 00:24:01.771
Starting today, you must repay his debt.

00:24:07.438 --> 00:24:08.646
Prepare yourself.

00:24:09.355 --> 00:24:12.313
This debt… is heavy as hell.

00:24:15.188 --> 00:24:16.230
FIRE-TIPPED SPEAR

00:24:16.313 --> 00:24:17.230
QIANKUN HOOP

00:24:17.313 --> 00:24:18.271
RED ARMILLARY SASH

00:24:18.355 --> 00:24:19.605
NINE DRAGONS DIVINE FIRE BARRIER

00:24:24.688 --> 00:24:25.813
QIANKUN HOOP

00:24:25.896 --> 00:24:27.896
He said that
after I use up these milk caps,

00:24:27.980 --> 00:24:30.813
my debt would be cleared
and my parents reincarnated.

00:24:30.896 --> 00:24:32.646
Three thousand and six hundred of them.

00:24:33.688 --> 00:24:36.730
It's been over a decade.
It'll all be over soon.

00:24:38.271 --> 00:24:42.146
So you talk to the Third Crown Prince
through that bird?

00:24:42.230 --> 00:24:44.021
And beat up whoever he tells you to?

00:24:44.105 --> 00:24:45.146
Pretty much.

00:24:45.230 --> 00:24:48.021
Like religious con-men
or malevolent ghosts.

00:24:49.938 --> 00:24:50.771
Happy now?

00:24:51.271 --> 00:24:52.646
Go turn on the computers.

00:24:53.230 --> 00:24:54.438
Okay.

00:24:55.646 --> 00:24:58.896
So you beat up people too?
I thought you only beat up ghosts.

00:24:59.563 --> 00:25:02.813
You get good and bad people.
It's the same with ghosts.

